## DeFi Math Formulas

### Constant Product AMM
```
x * y = k (invariant)
dy = y - k/(x + dx)
Price Impact = dx / (x + dx)
```

### Compound Interest
```
A = P(1 + r/n)^(nt)
APY = (1 + APR/n)^n - 1
```

### Liquidation Math
```
Health Factor = (Collateral * LTV) / Debt
Liquidation when HF < 1
```

