| **Primary** | WebFlux controllers, reactive streams, R2DBC |
| **Secondary** | Backpressure, reactive security, SSE/WebSocket |
| **Out of Scope** | Blocking MVC (‚Üí 02-spring-mvc), traditional JDBC |

