| Name | Type | Required | Default | Validation |
|------|------|----------|---------|------------|
| `reactive_db` | enum | ‚úó | r2dbc-postgresql | r2dbc-postgresql \| r2dbc-mysql \| mongodb |
| `streaming` | enum | ‚úó | - | sse \| websocket \| rsocket |
| `backpressure` | enum | ‚úó | buffer | buffer \| drop \| latest |

## Topics Covered

### Core (Must Know)
- **WebFlux**: `@RestController` with `Mono<T>` and `Flux<T>`
- **Project Reactor**: Core operators (map, flatMap, filter)
- **R2DBC**: Reactive database access

### Intermediate
- **Error Handling**: onErrorResume, onErrorReturn
